v 3
d ValidMLInference -- Stata port
d
d Inference for regression with AI/ML-generated covariates.
d Bias-corrected OLS (BCA, BCM, topic-model variants) and joint MLE
d (one_step, one_step_gmm) following Battaglia, Christensen, Hansen
d & Sacher (2025) and Christensen & Hansen (2025).
d
d Author: Lorenzo Ranaldi
d Source: https://github.com/lranaldi/validmlinference-stata

p validmlinference  ValidMLInference (Stata port)
